title: Top 9 Characters of AHS Apocalypse
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I feel like the warlocks’ death was unwarranted along with poor Zoe and Queenie, but then again the show is full of unwarranted deaths
Myrtle deserves better than five. She was fire this season!

There's No Luv for John Henry?,  I know he Died Twice in the Show But someone add him!!  Lol.  I thought he was the Smartest of the Warlocks, especially when it came to Michael Langdon, his motivation toward  stopping Michael started off great even though it led to his sudden death, His come back was Great, he had information and Had one of the Best moments in the season,.  Burning his Brother Warlocks and Ms. Meeds
I wish we got more Tate and Queenie...
I think we’ve seen a warlock in coven back when Fiona became supreme when Ana Leigh was killed by her they said no witch or warlock can detect her life force
